metadata.name: Anubis The White
metadata.description:
Unleash the power of Anubis The White NFT, your ticket to the enthralling Crypto Pharaohs World! 

This exclusive NFT grants you Level 1 membership and immerses you in a realm where ancient Egypt's magic and wonder collide with modern technology, art, and community. 

Embrace your destiny with Anubis The White NFT, and join a thriving community on a journey to protect the reign of Egyptian kings and make the world a better place.
